# Tailwind CSS Styling Guidelines

## Utility-First Approach

- Brug Tailwind utility classes direkte i JSX
- Undgå custom CSS klasser når Tailwind utilities kan bruges
- Gruppér relaterede utilities logisk (layout, spacing, colors, etc.)

```tsx
// ✅ Brug Tailwind utilities
<div className="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-zinc-50">
  <main className="flex w-full max-w-3xl flex-col gap-6 p-8">
    {/* content */}
  </main>
</div>

// ❌ Undgå custom CSS når ikke nødvendigt
<div className="custom-container">
  {/* content */}
</div>
```

## Responsive Design

- Brug Tailwind's responsive prefixes (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`, `2xl:`)
- Mobile-first approach - base styles er for mobile, tilføj breakpoints for større skærme
- Test på forskellige skærmstørrelser

```tsx
// ✅ Mobile-first responsive
<div className="flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 sm:flex-row sm:gap-6 sm:p-8 lg:gap-8">
  <div className="w-full sm:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

## Dark Mode Support

- Projektet understøtter dark mode via `dark:` prefix
- Brug `dark:` variant for alle farver der skal ændres i dark mode
- Test både light og dark mode

```tsx
// ✅ Dark mode support
<div className="bg-white text-black dark:bg-black dark:text-zinc-50">
  <h1 className="text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50">
    Title
  </h1>
  <p className="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
    Description
  </p>
</div>
```

## Color Palette

- Brug Tailwind's default color palette (zinc, slate, etc.)
- Konsistent brug af farver gennem projektet
- Brug semantiske farver (fx `bg-primary`, `text-secondary`) hvis defineret i `globals.css`

```tsx
// ✅ Konsistent color usage
<button className="bg-zinc-950 text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-50 dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-zinc-200">
  Click me
</button>
```

## Spacing og Layout

- Brug Tailwind's spacing scale (4, 8, 12, 16, etc.) for konsistens
- Brug `gap-*` for spacing i flex/grid layouts
- Brug `p-*` (padding) og `m-*` (margin) konsekvent

```tsx
// ✅ Konsistent spacing
<div className="flex flex-col gap-6 p-8">
  <section className="mb-4">
    {/* content */}
  </section>
</div>
```

## Typography

- Brug Tailwind's typography utilities (`text-*`, `font-*`)
- Projektet bruger Geist fonts defineret i `layout.tsx`
- Brug semantiske heading sizes (`text-3xl` for h1, `text-xl` for h2, etc.)

```tsx
// ✅ Typography
<h1 className="text-3xl font-semibold leading-10 tracking-tight">
  Main Title
</h1>
<p className="text-lg leading-8">
  Body text
</p>
```

## Component Styling Patterns

### Card Components

```tsx
// ✅ Card pattern
<div className="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900">
  {/* card content */}
</div>
```

### Button Components

```tsx
// ✅ Button patterns
<button className="rounded-full bg-zinc-950 px-5 py-3 text-white transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-50 dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-zinc-200">
  Primary Button
</button>

<button className="rounded-full border border-zinc-200 px-5 py-3 transition-colors hover:border-transparent hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800">
  Secondary Button
</button>
```

### Form Elements

- Brug `@tailwindcss/forms` plugin hvis tilføjet til projektet
- Konsistent styling på inputs, selects, checkboxes

```tsx
// ✅ Form input
<input
  type="text"
  className="w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-4 py-2 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900"
/>
```

## Image Optimization

- Brug Next.js `Image` komponent med Tailwind classes
- Definer width/height eksplicit for bedre performance
- Brug `dark:invert` for SVG logos der skal flippes i dark mode

```tsx
import Image from 'next/image';

<Image
  src="/logo.svg"
  alt="Logo"
  width={100}
  height={20}
  className="dark:invert"
  priority // Hvis above-the-fold
/>
```

## Custom CSS

- Placer custom CSS i `src/app/globals.css`
- Brug CSS custom properties (CSS variables) for dynamiske værdier
- Undgå custom CSS når Tailwind utilities kan bruges

```css
/* ✅ Custom CSS kun når nødvendigt */
@layer utilities {
  .custom-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
  }
}
```

## Animation og Transitions

- Brug Tailwind's transition utilities (`transition-*`)
- Brug `hover:`, `focus:`, `active:` states konsekvent
- Overvej Framer Motion for komplekse animationer (som nævnt i README)

```tsx
// ✅ Transitions
<button className="transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800">
  Hover me
</button>

<div className="transition-transform hover:scale-105">
  Hover scale
</div>
```

## Accessibility

- Brug semantiske HTML elementer
- Sørg for kontrast ratios (Tailwind's farver er designet til dette)
- Brug `focus:` states for keyboard navigation

```tsx
// ✅ Accessible button
<button
  className="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-zinc-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
  aria-label="Close dialog"
>
  Close
</button>
```

## Performance

- Undgå for mange nested divs - brug semantiske elementer
- Brug `@apply` sparsomt i custom CSS (kan øge bundle size)
- Prefer utility classes over custom CSS for bedre tree-shaking

